    Root kpt package for RKE2 cluster Kubernetes manifests.

    Organized by functional layers:
    - ha: High availability components (kube-vip)
    - mesh: Mesh networking (headscale, tailscale)
    - networking: Network policies, gateways, ingress (cilium-config, cilium, envoy-gateway, traefik)
    - runtime: Container runtimes (flox-containerd-shim)
    - storage: Storage solutions (openebs-zfs)
    - gitops: GitOps control plane and package management (flux, porch)
    - cicd: CI/CD components (tekton)
    - replication: Replicator services/CRDs
